<h1>SOCIAL ACTIVITIES</h1>
 
    <br>          
<h1>Tuesday, August 2</h1>
<p><strong>Welcome Reception</strong></p> 
<p>A light reception will be held at the end of the day on Tuesday August 2, at UC Irvine.</p>
    <br>
<hr size=7 width=100%>
    
<h1>Wednesday, August 3</h1>
<p><strong>Banquet Dinner</strong></p>

<p class="texto">Full conference registrants are invited to a Banquet Dinner at <a target="_blank" href="http://www.newportdunes.com/">Newport Dunes</a> on Wednesday August 3. Newport Dunes is located on Newport Bay and is adjacent to the Hyatt Regency Hotel - you can walk to the dinner in just a few minutes. <strong>Dinner will be held in the Bayview Room.</strong></p>
    
    <br>
    <hr size=7 width=100%>
<h1>Thursday, August 4</h1>
<p><strong>Poster Session</strong></p>
<p>A poster session with a light reception will close the day on Thursday, August 4.</p>

    
    <br>
    <hr size=7 width=100%>
<h1>Friday, August 5</h1>

<p>Visit to Google Irvine</p>
<p>On Friday afternoon, the <strong>conference shuttle bus will take us to Google in Irvine for a site visit</strong>.</p>

